-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">Q</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">：</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">什么时候能玩这套阵容</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">？</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">●&nbsp;</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">开局</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">有</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">3/4炼金或有符文</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">底城争夺战、小小巨人火、巨型泰坦</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">可冲。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">●&nbsp;</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">另一种连胜炼金</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">，是开局没有3炼金，但强度能连胜，且装备契合史密奇或希尔科，有4炼金后再考虑走连败。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">Q</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">：</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">炼金怎么玩</b><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></b></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><img src=\"https://k6.tgl.qq.com/tft/cover/20250227/06ebce35f151622849cd88f661c31c67_1740653079.png\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></b></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">● 版本更新后虽说没有了炼金转职，但4/5炼金连败获得微光变多，相对没更新前来说虽说开炼金更难，但想达成500/600层其实比上版本容易了一些。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">如</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">开局3炼金</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">有</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">底层争夺战</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">，</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">3-5</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">能</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">找到希尔科</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">开出5炼金，</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">12连败</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">能</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">稳定600层收菜，</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">且600层收菜大概率拿到</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">2星塞薇卡</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://k6.tgl.qq.com/tft/cover/20250227/23fa9a9aa42561597077b721ed254365_1740653088.png\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">但当前</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">500层收菜</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">其实强度没有上版本稳定，当前测试中感觉如完美装出完美烈性病毒，吃鸡概率比较大，其次是</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">完美</b><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">军刀</b><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">与</b><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">毒素倾泻</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">，强度不算高，但只要运气不算太差基本能有分，而入史密奇3星有</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">完美链锯刃或割肉</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">，也能大概率前二。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">而其他装备强度非常一般，非常建议用重铸器砸掉，可以说当前想玩炼金稳，还是建议在有</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">符文</b><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">底城争夺战、小小巨人火、巨型泰坦</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">在冲。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">● 炼金装备分配</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">完美烈性病毒</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">建议给予</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">希尔科。</b><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></b></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-