px;\">。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">完美军刀</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">建议给予</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">希尔科，也可给予塞薇卡或史密奇</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">增伤+高续航。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">完美微光绽放：</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">建议给予3星</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">荏妮</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">。</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></b></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">完美皮城海克斯护甲</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">：建议给予3星</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">荏妮，希尔科</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">有续航装也可用。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0