 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">装备优先级</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">：朔极之矛/饮血→泰坦→朔极之矛/正义→珠光→其他。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://k6.tgl.qq.com/tft/cover/20250227/720d5073cd4e67b9a28b61fc95f76e61_1740653147.png\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">●&nbsp;</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">符文方面最优</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">：</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">底城争夺战、最小巨人、巨形泰坦、羁绊：意外搭档、炽热灵魂</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">●&nbsp;</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">其他</b><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">也可考虑</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">：</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">王王冠意志、发条增速器、装备收集器、权杖意志、透体莲花、炽热灵魂、健康就是财富、激昂墓志铭、便携锻炉、大百宝袋、嗜火、耐心学习/纷乱头脑/天降金币、双排、英勇福袋（追3星史密奇才考虑）等。。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">● 异常突变：</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">通常给拿到完美炼金装备得棋子找异常突变，</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">希尔科</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">法强回蓝类，</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">史密奇/塞薇卡</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">增伤战力类。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">希尔科：绝不浪费、魔法专家、主脑、培养魔法、法强吸收等。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">史密奇/塞薇卡：狂战之怒、恕瑞玛的传承、翻盘故事、最后机会、深入敌阵、隐形、物理专家、地下拳王、护甲山崩、攻击吸收、攻击上升等</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span><img src=\"https://k6.tgl.qq.com/tft/cover/20250227/6144a65ee761dbb30b0bfde409543dce_1740653159.png\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">● 开局有3、4炼金直接上，走连败，没有就走连胜。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">● 3-1/2升6人口，看情况补2先知或2哨兵，保证连败可适当上装备。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://k6.tgl.qq.com/tft/cover/20250227/70469160f261043ecd2e0607303424ff_1740653175.png\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">● 3-5升7人口，大搜卡找到希尔科开出5炼金，如经济优质可3-5直接拉8人口找希尔科。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">小贴士：选秀时候有希尔科必拿。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">● 升8后补蒙多、俄洛伊或艾克，</span><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">收菜后开6炼金</b><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">。如史密奇3星可开高伏击。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span><img src=\"https://k6.tgl.qq.com/tft/cover/20250227/6cd495d1af38f88304690c2b452dcf47_1740653191.png\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">● 升9人口后补兰博，莫德凯撒可换下蒙多就好。</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://k6.tgl.qq.com/tft/cover/20250227/6ad05e9121bdf0696398dc4b88f3ea0b_1740653210.png\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 26px; padding-bottom: 25px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\"><b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">阵容码</b>与详细攻略，请微信公众号关注<b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px;\">摩昂解说或摩昂金铲铲！</b></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"foot-wrap\" id=\"footWrap\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; width: 1903px; min-width: 1230px; padding-top: 45px; padding-bottom: 45px; background-color: rgb(227, 226, 226); color: rgb(159, 147, 120); font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: tahoma, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"foot_inner\" id=\"gfooter\" ams=\"152/35206/m131\" age=\"16\" dark=\"1\" ieg-logo=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; max-width: 1358px; min-width: 1230px; height: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; overflow: hidden; position: relative;\"><div class=\"foot foot_dark\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 20px; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; min-width: 1050px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"></div></div></div>','兄弟们好，我是你们的上分助手摩昂，今天摩昂给兄弟们带来的是S13赛季娱乐阵容炼金的阵容思路。\n\n阵容一图流在最后，但建议看完阵容思路分析，能理解阵容思路，才更容易掌控阵容，更容易上大分。\n\n阵容码与详细攻略，请微信公众号关注摩昂解说或摩昂金铲铲！','http://localhost:9090/files/1740978100127-651f69bec1c1ccce54e7f5a1249ff8e.png','[\"PC游戏\",\"主机游戏\"]',1,'2025-03-03',2,18),(145,'我买的枪皮为啥装不了？','<p><img src=\"http://localhost:9090/files/1740980100918-d9c22f90b7348167ade9305782b49c4.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/></p>','套装里单独买的枪皮，为啥显示道具暂不可用？','http://localhost:9090/files/1740980164864-e67e01236169dba46df4b1810ed878d.png','[\"PC游戏\",\"主机游戏\"]',1,'2025-03-03',13,21);
